com.ephesoft.gxt.systemconfig.client.presenter.application.regexbuilder

Class RegexFieldDetailPresenter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ephesoft.gxt.core.client.BasePresenter<SystemConfigController,V>
      • com.ephesoft.gxt.systemconfig.client.presenter.SystemConfigInlinePresenter<RegexFieldDetailView>
        • com.ephesoft.gxt.systemconfig.client.presenter.application.regexbuilder.RegexFieldDetailPresenter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BindHandler, com.google.gwt.event.shared.EventHandler

    public class RegexFieldDetailPresenter
extends SystemConfigInlinePresenter<RegexFieldDetailView>
    Provides the functionality to handle events for RegexFieldDetailView. This presenter handles the events for the text section of the regex builder.
    Version:
    1.0 $LastChangedDate:$
    $LastChangedRevision:$
